KIDNAPINGS -- MEXICO; DRUG ENFORCEMENT OFFICERS; DRUG ENFORCEMENT 
ADMINISTRATION; ALVAREZ MACHAIN, HUMBERTO; CAMARENA, ENRIQUE 
</P>
