ROMANIA -- GOVERNMENT; ROMANIA -- POLITICS; COUNCIL OF THE FRONT OF NATIONAL 
SALVATION; ILIESCU, ION; ROMANIA -- ELECTIONS; DEMOCRACY 
</P>
