parking structure can become gripped by gridlock. One tip, officials say, is to 
hunt for a spot in a surface lot on the south side of the terminal. It is often 
overlooked by motorists dashing along the airport's loop road. AURELIO JOSE 
BARRERA / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
