</P>
<P>
Western Christian 1, Santa Margarita 0 -- Visiting Western Christian (15-4) 
scored an unearned run with the help of three errors in the fifth. Santa 
Margarita had a runner thrown out at the plate for the final out of the sixth 
inning. 
</P>
<P>
