<TEXT>
<P>
I recently read an article on black people of Orange County (May 10). I was 
shocked to read some of the statements said about black people. 
</P>
<P>
I feel it was misleading information to make black people even less desirable 
in white society. 
</P>
<P>
All of your statements were from black people, (who) are confused in their way 
