<P>
FREE TAPED BOOKS OFFERED AT LIBRARIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
It was interesting to read Dennis McLellan's article on the Rental Book Tape 
business (May 12). 
</P>
<P>
But I was saddened to note the omissions of coverage of free taped books in 
public libraries throughout the country serving hundreds of thousands of 
