<HEADLINE>
<P>
CHERUB-BIN THRIFT SHOP SEEKS DONATIONS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Donations of clothing, appliances, furniture and household goods are being 
sought by the Cherub-Bin Thrift Shop to raise money for Pacific Clinics. 
</P>
<P>
The Cherub-Bin sells the donated items and gives the proceeds to Pacific 
Clinics, a nonprofit, community-based mental-health agency that provides 
outpatient services to children, adults, senior citizens and the homeless of 
the San Gabriel Valley. 
</P>
<P>
All donations are tax deductible. 
</P>
<P>
The Cherub-Bin Thrift Shop is located at 909 S. Fair Oaks Ave., Pasadena. For 
pickup or more information, call (818) 792-4362 between 10 a.m. and 4 p.m. 
</P>
